## Analysis Period: September 2024 - March 2025

---

## Executive Summary

600519 (Kweichow Moutai) has experienced a significant multi-month correction followed by early signs of stabilization. The stock reached a high of approximately ¥1,660 in late September 2024, followed by a sharp 27% decline to around ¥1,200 by mid-October. Since then, the stock has been trading in a broad consolidation range between ¥1,350-¥1,500, with recent momentum suggesting a potential trend reversal.

